properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 4 at 2:41PM CST until January 5 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected.

* WHERE...North St. Louis, Central St. Louis, Southern Lake,
Northern Aitkin, South Aitkin, Carlton and South St. Louis and
Pine Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Fond du
Lac Band, the Mille Lacs Band, Lena Lake, Big Sandy Lake, East
Lake and, Hinckley areas and the Bois Forte Band, Nett Lake
and, Lake Vermillion areas.

* WHEN...From 7 AM to 6 PM CST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and some power outages may result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM TO 6 PM CST SUNDAY
